        <span>/</span>
        <span>Finding a song/poem/story seems to work fine.</span>
        <span>4/5</span>

        <span>4</span>
        <span>1</span>
        <span>/</span>
        <span
          >We had to tell the test is over, so that part wasn’t exactly clear</span
        >
        <span>3/5</span>

        <span>1</span>
        <span>2</span>
        <span>/</span>
        <span>Instructions clear.</span>
        <span>5/5</span>

        <span>2</span>
