        <span>/</span>
        <span>Found the button without a problem.</span>
        <span>5/5</span>

        <span>1</span>
        <span>3</span>
        <span>/</span>
        <span
          >Instructions seemed clear. A bit of hesitation before starting.</span
        >
        <span>4/5</span>

        <span>2</span>
        <span>3</span>
        <span>“Euu hey euu i don’t know what to say haha”</span>
        <span>They started the recording before they made up their mind.</span>
        <span>3/5</span>

        <span>3</span>
        <span>3</span>
        <span>/</span>
        <span
          >The didn't realise they had to speak out loud when reading the poem</span
        >
        <span>2/5</span>

        <span>4</span>
        <span>3</span>
        <span>“How do I stop?”</span>
        <span
          >Stopping was hard as well. Buttons weren't clear for this person.</span
        >
        <span>2/5</span>

        <span>1</span>
        <span>4</span>
        <span
          >“Yes ofcourse I would send voice memos, it’s a beautiful and original
          concept”</span
        >
        <span
          >Said that but didn't actually turn to the ipad or interact with it
          much</span
        >
        <span>0/5</span>

        <span>2</span>
        <span>4</span>
        <span>/</span>
        <span
          >They started talking to us about the concept. The idea of the test
          didn't seem clear.</span
        >
        <span>0/5</span>

        <span>3</span>
        <span>4</span>
        <span>/</span>
